# WarcLock

> **A wardriving pocket watch with style.**

**By Deamonmist**

![status](https://img.shields.io/badge/status-1.0.0--beta.1-orange) ![platform](https://img.shields.io/badge/MCU-XIAO%20ESP32--C5-blue) ![updated](https://img.shields.io/badge/updated-June%2015%2C%202026-lightgrey)

A portable war-driver built from basic components that passes as a nifty home-made analog clock. It shows the real time on a round TFT face with a satellite-connection indicator, battery gauge, active-wardriving indicator, and random messages — all wrapped in a digital Art Deco style.

